re slippage.  This condition can vary by terrain type.</comment><data>{"commentRefs":[],"fieldData":{"~commentOffsetX":"16","~commentOffsetY":"16"}}</data><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id=",bkzh;sO6?Qv%j0Pty`u"><field name="NUM">20</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="bF8sKwI[2jr`Dh!|cBKy"><field name="VAR" id="Pn4_q~v_/TkrLShW@pU.">accel_rate</field><comment pinned="false" h="109" w="459">This variable controls the rate of the acceleration ramp-- how long the bot takes to get from zero to max. In initial testing 1 worked well, 2 produced tire slippage.</comment><data>{"commentRefs":[],"fieldData":{"~commentOffsetX":"16","~commentOffsetY":"16"}}</data><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="asKaE+ip1[bd=o!ia4-~"><field name="NUM">5</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="Hw8!_|~-@[qDev0a5^Ig"><field name="VAR" id="`=ApUrD}(0qDd^Yp4(rh">max_normal_speed</field><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="alY[qdOzWMzc#WA1bi~F"><field name="NUM">99</field></shadow></value><next><block type="quest_Note_1_quest_Show_String_For_Note_Small_Func" id="x0k:2%0c1w]|6(S[JHE:"><value name="textStrIn"><shadow type="text" id="7muK/a;dY*G3br6XYZKm"><field name="TEXT">For Swim Bot, "Turbo" drops speed for slower maneuvers</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="LmfwggyKRe!CN*PTHtg?"><field name="VAR" id="Bdy2d{-@DtkKH1)=c_,-">max_turbo_speed</field><comment pinned="false" h="119" w="369">This value will determine the maximum speed to which the bot will accelerate before topping out. Valid range is 0 to 100.</comment><data>{"commentRefs":[],"fieldData":{"~commentOffsetX":"16","~commentOffsetY":"16"}}</data><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="=r}_Kl}0NytoJW9[/1=4"><field name="NUM">60</field></shadow></value><next><block type="quest_Note_4_quest_Show_String_For_Note_Small_Func" id="4p?]^7rKP~|6[3_B7ouo"><value name="textStrIn"><shadow type="text" id="WhWpg1T4Ij{:=zNQfh